claim.claim-text:
10. A substrate quantification method comprising the steps of: 
preparing an analytical element comprising a cavity for accommodating a sample, a working electrode and a counter electrode exposed to an inside of said cavity, a reagent layer which comprises at least an oxidoreductase and is formed inside or in the vicinity of said cavity, an opening communicating with said cavity and a member covering said opening; 
supplying the sample to said analytical element to react a substrate contained in the sample with said oxidoreductase; 
closing said opening; 
applying a voltage between said working electrode and said counter electrode; and 
detecting a change in electric signal between said working electrode and said counter electrode upon said voltage application.
